```

Both are then re-exported from their `src/index.ts`:
- `/Users/jeevanpillay/Code/@lightfastai/lightfast/api/app/src/index.ts:12` — `export { createCallerFactory } from "./trpc";`
- `/Users/jeevanpillay/Code/@lightfastai/lightfast/api/platform/src/index.ts:27` — `export { createCallerFactory } from "./trpc";`

`platformRouter.createCaller(ctx)` is how `createCaller` is actually invoked in practice — `createCallerFactory` is exported but the packages that own the caller logic call `.createCaller()` directly on the router instance (as seen in `packages/platform-trpc/src/caller.ts:28`).

